    "description": "Surreal Farm is a charming farm simulator that invites players into a vibrant and colorful world where creativity and strategy combine. In this enchanting game, you’ll start with a humble plot of land, where you’ll plant, harvest, and sell crops, raise quirky farm animals, and expand your farm into the largest and most prosperous in the region.<br><br>As you progress, you’ll unlock a variety of unusual crops, fantastical animals, and magical farm tools that add a touch of the surreal to your farming experience. The key to success in Surreal Farm is not just how efficiently you manage your resources, but also how creatively you design your farm. Every choice you make influences your farm's growth and productivity.<br><br>The game features a relaxed, casual gameplay style that’s easy to pick up but offers enough depth to keep you engaged as your farm grows. With its charming cartoon graphics, playful animations, and a whimsical soundtrack, Surreal Farm is designed to be a delightful escape into a world where the biggest and most imaginative farm wins.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLANT CROPS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180960/extras/a46453aad444d048f67de2ce358c31e3.poster.avif?t=1726210883\" width=678 height=508 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180960/extras/a46453aad444d048f67de2ce358c31e3.webm?t=1726210883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIND UNIQUE ANIMALS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180960/extras/e33a69fffd9baafd5b95fc35b35d0e26.poster.avif?t=1726210883\" width=665 height=625 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/s